WEBVTT

00:01.334 --> 00:03.201
¶ I take two steps forward ¶

00:03.269 --> 00:05.670
¶ I take two steps back... ¶

00:05.772 --> 00:08.640
Paula Abdul really
knows how to pick a man.

00:08.741 --> 00:11.075
¶ And you know
it ain't fiction ¶

00:11.144 --> 00:12.177
I love her.

00:12.245 --> 00:13.778
She doesn't know
you're alive.

00:13.846 --> 00:15.346
Well, that's going
to change.

00:15.414 --> 00:17.148
I know some people
in high places

00:17.216 --> 00:18.483
who have some friends

00:18.550 --> 00:20.618
who told me
her number's on the Internet.

00:20.653 --> 00:23.255
¶ She makes the bed... ¶

00:23.322 --> 00:26.057
Oh, lord, she ran
into a wall again.

00:26.159 --> 00:28.426
No. She's taking
waltzing lessons.

00:28.494 --> 00:29.995
It is a great way
to exercise.

00:30.062 --> 00:32.597
I'm just having trouble
finding a partner.

00:32.698 --> 00:33.665
Zelda?

00:33.733 --> 00:36.101
I don't plan on being
reduced to dancing

00:36.168 --> 00:39.070
with my sister until
they put us in the home.

00:39.172 --> 00:41.806
I've got to talk to Harvey--
no time for eating.

00:41.908 --> 00:43.108
How about a waltz?

00:43.176 --> 00:45.777
Uh, how about no?

00:45.878 --> 00:47.979
She kissed Josh
last night

00:48.046 --> 00:49.381
and Harvey saw them.

00:49.415 --> 00:52.784
What?! And no one called me
at waltz class to tell me?

00:52.852 --> 00:55.620
¶ We come together
'cause opposites attract ¶

00:55.655 --> 00:57.855
I want that!

00:57.923 --> 01:00.091
¶ It ain't fiction,
just a natural fact... ¶

01:00.159 --> 01:01.359
There.

01:01.427 --> 01:02.560
Great.

01:02.628 --> 01:03.961
A fake talking cat.

01:04.029 --> 01:06.063
Just what we need around here.

01:06.099 --> 01:08.666
So Sabrina kissed Josh,
and Harvey saw them?

01:08.734 --> 01:09.934
Tell me everything.

01:10.036 --> 01:11.269
That's everything.

01:11.337 --> 01:12.536
¶ ...'Cause opposites attract ¶

01:12.671 --> 01:14.538
¶ And you know,
it ain't fiction ¶

01:14.606 --> 01:17.042
¶ Just a natural fact ¶

01:17.143 --> 01:18.310
You go, girl.

01:18.377 --> 01:19.878
¶ We come together
'cause opposites... ¶

01:20.746 --> 01:22.714
¶ ¶

